    "Hence, solving (4) and (8) using SQP under the same Hessian approximation in Eq.",
    "(5a) leads to the exact same iterates.",
    "This is the case for Hessian approximations that do not depend on secondorder information of the dynamics, such as the generalized Gauss-Newton approximation.",
